title: Rebirth Of a Cute Wife
description: In the previous life, Ye Ling was killed by Mo lengqing. After reborn, she has become Mo lengqing's wife. Ye Ling hates Mo Leng Qing, upgrading all the way. She even disguised herself as a man and became the male god in the entertainment. But did not expect that the man trapped her in the corner: "I can recognize you although you changed identity."
